Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.47,0:01:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Rain, rain, rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.34,0:01:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should skip school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.62,0:01:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's wrong with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.77,0:02:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems to be feeling low these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my, it's you, Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How long have you been there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this "Oh, my, it's you, Yui"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I knocked on your door several times, and you didn't answer,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,so I came in to wake you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wondering why you woke up on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's why it's raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's {\i1}that{\i0\fscx150} {\r}supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to rain all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:03:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui doesn't seem to have a care in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.60,0:03:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say something?\N Oh, you don't want breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I should clean the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you be quieter on the stairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.09,0:03:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Strawberry pattern...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please explain that part, will you, Mizuno-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuno-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is a smart student like\N Mizuno at a loss for words?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.31,0:04:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's wrong with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're worried, why don't you go talk to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She's your childhood friend, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not... mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomomi-san is our neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also worried about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She's feeling low these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't {\i1}you{\i0\fscx150} {\r}talk to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be easier for her to talk to another girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.18,0:05:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't seem to like me that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you'd better talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does Tomomi hate you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomomi isn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What an insensitive man Makoto is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't know a girl's secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui-san and Tomomi-san happen to live close to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're misinterpreting the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.88,0:05:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Saionji Aritomo, will save you from that misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Aritomo doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,From this angle, he looks like an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You got turned down, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.69,0:05:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The two most insensitive men of Yasohachi Academy are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Before their stupidity infects me, I should leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You get treated like that because you're always chasing girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try sports instead? Sports!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Devote yourself to club\N activity... and sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The sweat of adolescence!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That will be a beautiful memory of your school life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Makoto, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking of going home, but then it started raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Does your body melt in the rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui probably has a folding umbrella in her locker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui... Narusawa... Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:23.17,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(344,44)\fnOne Stroke Script LET\c&H161D21&\bord0\frz6\fax-0.07\fsp0\be1}Narusawa Yui
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's locked...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If I use this to fiddle with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's open. It's open!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Acting like a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shame on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean,\N "What are you doing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just borrowing Yui's umbrella to take home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A man shouldn't open a girl's locker without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention that it's Narusawa Yui's locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What wrong, Akira? You're blushing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He broke her locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui will be mad about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it. She {\i1}did{\i0\fscx150} {\r}have an umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, that's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.47,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25}Sign: Yasohachigaoka
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Makoto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.49,0:09:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Yui-chan's umbrella?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we walk home together?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You used to tease me\N and make me cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of times, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! I don't remember anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.91,0:09:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Not true! You just said,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"You're always nice."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That just popped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You were a bully.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a feminist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're in any sort of trouble, you can talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so embarrassed that I can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain didn't stop even after midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The awkwardness between Yui and me remained,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,so I had to eat dinner alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and I had nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You look troubled, young man. Drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's whiskey.{That's a really big glass, and with ice too. Yuck!}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Irish whiskey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Alcohol is alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Alcohol is the best of all medicines.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It cures everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A troubled young man should drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm telling you, every man must find his own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:12:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Misako-san, you're quite drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not drunk at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm telling you, every man should live as he pleases.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,On his own...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,On his own...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignoring women's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee. You were drinking all night with Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got some nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't shout at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a hangover and maybe a cold too. My head aches.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you get for...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,sleeping on the floor in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Justice has been served.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My head aches.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.02,0:12:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:12:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.18,0:13:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to throw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.22,0:13:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Look there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to throw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop complaining and look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomomi. And she's with Yoshiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm delighted that you asked me for a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.97,0:13:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then ten thirty on Sunday,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of Studio Ataru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bee.{he's saying bye bye in a weird way}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Skip, skip, oh, I can skip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A date?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's with Yoshiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bee.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, amazing things can happen between boys and girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Mom told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all men, it's Yoshiki!\N How could that happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.38,0:14:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No. No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Yoshiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,0:14:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Yoshiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be half asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I didn't hit him that h-hard, guys, right, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I just poked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a dream. I'm glad it was a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomomi-chan, you're naughty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Naughty...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a good opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei. I, Nagaoka Yoshiki, have cleared the hurdle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you angry because \NI didn't make lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,About this morning and that dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.11,0:15:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream? A bad feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.87,0:16:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:16.53,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(334,74)\c&H29272C&\3c&HCDC1C8&\bord0.7\frx20\fs25}Photography Club
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:19.04,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H111F21&\3c&HCDC1C8&\bord0\b1\fs20\pos(582,131)\be1}Photography\N Club
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it. That was a prophetic dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My hunch was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Yoshiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why Tomomi's so depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This angle...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.31,0:16:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He took this photo from my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.77,0:16:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you throw them\N around like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I visited your room when you happened to be away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, don't look at me with such a fierce expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:17:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't expecting to shoot photos like that from your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped by to deliver a photo of Yui-san and her youthful mother
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.95,0:17:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,at the spring Sports Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Misako-san really let you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She gave me delicious milk tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She said, "Please make yourself at home in Makoto's room until he comes back."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And by chance, I happened to look out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.16,0:17:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that Tomomi-san was your neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.33,0:17:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I was very lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,V-Violence is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you like the photo, I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a rare picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring you to justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The tickets for my date.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me all the negatives and any other pictures you have of Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.69,0:18:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you feeling all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We see each other every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be inappropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Yoshiki isn't coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me to give these to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:19:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he wouldn't follow you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.65,0:19:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.62,0:19:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it couldn't be true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That angle was from \Nyour room, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Your...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.69,0:20:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.98,0:20:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan wouldn't do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshiki got into Onii-chan's room while he was away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.35,0:20:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So Makoto-kun tells you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I just overheard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I was being nosy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.26,0:21:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm quite familiar with Makoto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.38,0:21:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Makoto-kun, you {\i1}are{\fscx150} {\r}nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.42,0:21:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We're childhood friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be just childhood friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.38,0:21:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to see me as a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.53,0:22:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.95,0:22:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that our town was this beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.02,0:22:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're beautiful too, Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.73,0:22:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see your beautiful figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.33,0:22:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.40,0:22:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you turn off the lights, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.49,0:22:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine{boobs} are small, and I get embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.60,0:22:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.33,0:22:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're not small.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.91,0:22:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now take your hand away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.27,0:22:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.77,0:22:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to hide it forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.30,0:22:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.08,0:22:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said that I'm a bully?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.09,0:22:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.36,0:22:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you promise not to laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:22:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I won't laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.87,0:23:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A man is as good as his word.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.45,0:23:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm embarrassed that \Nyou're looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.55,0:23:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to kill myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.90,0:23:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're as cute as a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.26,0:23:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.31,0:23:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? You don't dislike me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.02,0:23:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.07,0:23:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.98,0:23:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's soft here.{Not mention where just "here"}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.46,0:23:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you that sensitive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.28,0:23:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.27,0:23:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're responding so strongly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.11,0:23:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're always playing with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.91,0:23:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.10,0:23:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But this feels great.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.13,0:23:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Not that rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.40,0:23:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll break.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.75,0:23:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.53,0:24:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.51,0:24:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.56,0:24:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. Makoto-kun, hurry and come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.02,0:24:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Makoto, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.48,0:24:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.42,0:24:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.78,0:24:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.40,0:24:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.64,0:24:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I always dreamed of doing this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.64,0:24:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.73,0:24:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was a bit different than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.47,0:24:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,In my dream, you were rougher and more insistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.91,0:24:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't stop, even if I begged you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.09,0:24:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to be like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.42,0:25:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomomi, I'm going to be rough!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.25,0:25:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!{or Good!}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.25,0:25:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.99,0:25:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're beautiful, Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.30,0:25:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Makoto-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.78,0:25:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.24,0:25:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer vacation is starting tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.06,0:26:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but you mustn't be impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.80,0:26:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There are lots of temptations in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.76,0:26:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I hope you make good summer memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.53,0:26:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25}Sign: Yasohachi Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.53,0:26:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.40,0:26:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.22,0:26:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, beige!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.60,0:26:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.91,0:26:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.11,0:26:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You act like a brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.13,0:26:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are a brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.89,0:26:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch where you're walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.62,0:26:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is wrong with that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.68,0:26:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Onii-chan? I'm leaving you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.73,0:26:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Starting now,\N it's summer vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.97,0:27:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,600)\fnArtificeSSK\bord0\fs28\pos(449,416)\c&HBC6131&\be1}To be continued...
