Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.27,0:27:56.57,EdR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150}tsumetai ame no sora miage
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.14,0:27:52.27,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150}On an early spring afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.27,0:27:56.57,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150}I looked up at the sky in the cold rain
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.57,0:28:03.62,EdR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150}odoritaku naru youna kibun de aruita
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.57,0:28:03.62,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150}I walked with an urge to dance
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.53,0:28:18.13,EdR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150}arifureta nichijyou ni itsuka kokoro ga kumotte ta
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.53,0:28:18.13,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150}My heart was clouded by the familiar days
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.13,0:28:25.71,EdR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150}sonna koto sae kizukazu ni ita
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.13,0:28:25.71,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150}I didn't understand anything
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.65,0:28:29.66,EdR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150}keredo
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.65,0:28:29.66,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.98,0:28:40.00,EdR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150}honno sasayakana nandemo nai youna yuuki dakeredo
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.98,0:28:40.00,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150}It was a small piece of courage, almost like nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.00,0:28:47.22,EdR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150}sonna koto de naze ka sukoshi kokoro ga hareta
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.00,0:28:47.22,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150}I don't know why, but it brightened my heart a bit
